{"tid":2172278,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全球供應鏈在逐步移出中國，鴻海及和碩考慮在墨西哥設廠","createTime":"2020-08-24T13:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T14:37:03.000Z","uid":48040,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e1cc54bbca51958047e10650283dcaedd219c450","tid":2172278,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:15:27.000Z","msg":"路透引述消息人士報導，鴻海集團、和碩以及立訊精密等公司正考慮在墨西哥設立新廠，凸顯美中貿易戰和新冠肺炎疫情的衝擊，可能促使全球供應鏈更廣泛地逐步移出中國大陸。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，鴻海可能在今年稍晚就新廠議題做出最後決定，而後展開相關作業，這項計畫尚未定案，仍可能生變。消息人士稱，鴻海有意讓新設的工廠生產蘋果iPhone。另一位消息人士則表示，沒有跡象顯示蘋果直接參與這項計畫。蘋果公司暫未對此消息發表評論。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士另透露，和碩正與銀行就墨西哥增設工廠進行初步談判，該工廠將主要組裝晶片和其他電子元件。和碩拒絕置評。<br />\n<br />\n此外，立訊精密也考慮今年在墨西哥建設一家工廠，緩解美中關稅戰的衝擊。目前仍不清楚立訊精密考慮建設的產線。立訊精密也未回應置評請求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.reuters.com/article/china-us-covid-tw-hon-hai-mx-0824-idCNKBS25K1BV?il=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fchina-us-covid-tw-hon-hai-mx-0824-idCNKBS25K1BV%3Fil%3D0&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbobsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=4f64d950\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fchina-us-covid-tw-hon-hai-mx-0824-idCNKBS25K1BV%3Fil%3D0&h=e8e130aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.reuters.com/article/china-us-covid-tw-hon-hai-mx-0824-idCNKBS25K1BV?il=0</a>"},{"pid":"e8b05434f0b1d083a4eef6e512eaf45b9ec45a2c","tid":2172278,"uid":19126,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:30:14.000Z","msg":"冇哂洋鬼子生意，支那又成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6064e45685f0e1c6fcf9f716e25104e2a11b03a6","tid":2172278,"uid":48040,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e8b05434f0b1d083a4eef6e512eaf45b9ec45a2c","tid":2172278,"uid":19126,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:30:14.000Z","msg":"冇哂洋鬼子生意，支那又成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"不用為洋鬼